{"article_id":"HILnUYdqDaDQnn3g","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"British officials rebuked President Donald Trump on Friday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"for claiming","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that the individuals","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"responsible","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"for setting off explosives in the London subway","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"had been \" in the sights of \" law enforcement","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"who failed to be \" proactive . \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Prime Minister Theresa May reproached Trump for his rhetoric in the wake of what police are investigating as a terrorist attack","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that injured at least 29 people .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"\" I never think","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"it ' s helpful for anybody to speculate on what is an ongoing investigation , \"","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"she said .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" As I ' ve just said ,","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the police and security services are working","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"to discover the full circumstances of this cowardly attack","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"and to identify all those responsible . \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"Trump earlier on Friday had used the latest attack","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"to offer tough talk on terrorism ,","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"and implied","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that Scotland Yard officials had fallen down on the job","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"- although it ' s unclear what non-public information , if any ,","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"the president based the comment on .","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"\" Another attack in London by a loser terrorist , \"","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"Trump tweeted early Friday morning .","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"\" These are sick and demented people","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"who were in the sights of Scotland Yard .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"Must be proactive ! \"","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"He wrote in a follow-up post","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"that \" loser terrorists \" should \" be dealt with in a much tougher manner \"","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"and urged the U.S. to curb their internet access ,","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"which serves as a recruiting tool for terrorists .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Breaking News Alerts","depth":3},{"id":32,"text":"Get breaking news","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"when it happens -","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"in your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"Email Sign Up","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"By signing up","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"you agree to receive email newsletters or alerts from .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"You can unsubscribe at any time .","depth":6},{"id":39,"text":"National security adviser H.R . McMaster appeared to try to clean up Trump 's comment ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"telling reporters later on Friday afternoon","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"that Trump was speaking generally about Scotland Yard ,","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"and that he was trying to broadly convey","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"that law enforcement is focused on the threat of terrorism .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"\" For years , Scotland Yard has been a leader ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"as our FBI has been a leader .","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"So I think","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"if there was a terrorist attack here ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"God forbid ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"that we would say","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that they were in the sights of the FBI , \"","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"McMaster said .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"\" So I think","depth":5},{"id":53,"text":"he didn ' t mean anything beyond that . \"","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"Trump and his administration have stoked the ire of British officials before .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"The U.K. earlier this year temporarily ceased intelligence sharing with the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"after images from an attack in Manchester were leaked to and published in U.S. media ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"infuriating British officials .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"May had said","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"she would `` make clear to President Trump","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that intelligence","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"that is shared between our law enforcement agencies","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"must remain secure ''","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"when the two met at a NATO summit in May .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"Speak","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"ng in Brussels that month ,","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"rump condemned the `` deeply troubling '' leaks","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"nd said","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"e would ask the Justice Department to review the matter","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"nd prosecute the culprit ,","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"f appropriate .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"White House official said on Friday","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"hat chief of staff John Kelly wasn ' t with the president","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"hen he fired off his tweets about \" loser terrorists \" before 7 a.m.","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"elly has tried to bring structure to the West Wing","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"nd contain some of the president ' s impulses","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"y serving as a gatekeeper to what people and what information make it into the Oval Office .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"he official said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"t ' s unclear whether Kelly has spoken with the president about his tweets ,","depth":10},{"id":79,"text":"ut Trump was scheduled to receive an intelligence briefing later Friday morning .","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"ondon Mayor Sadiq Khan ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"ho clashed with Trump after an attack on the London Bridge area in June ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"aid on Friday","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"e been too busy working with police , security services and first responders","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"o pay attention to Trump ' s tweets .","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"I haven ' t had a chance","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"o look at Twitter ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"et alone tweet , \"","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"e said .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"Metropolitan Police spokesperson dismissed Trump ' s tweet in an interview with the Independent as \" speculation . \"","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"We don ' t even know","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"ho the suspects are","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"o it ' s a bit difficult to say , \"","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"he spokesperson said .","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"ick Timothy , a former aide to May , echoed the prime minister ' s sentiment .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"e said","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"he tweet is \" so unhelpful from leader of our ally and intelligence partner . \"","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"rump told reporters in the Rose Garden later Friday morning","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"hat the attack is \" a terrible thing \"","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"nd reiterated his calls for America to \" be very smart \"","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"nd get \" very , very tough . \"","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"We ' re not nearly tough enough , \"","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"aid Trump ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"ho added","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"hat he would call May on Friday .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"That is just an absolutely terrible thing . \"","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"ay offered her thoughts to \" those injured at Parsons Green and emergency services","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"ho are responding bravely to this terrorist incident \"","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"n her initial statement .","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"s of late Friday morning , Trump hadn ' t publicly offered his thoughts and prayers or pledged America ' s support to London ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"ut the White House said","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"e did so privately in a call with May .","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"rump conveyed \" his sympathies and prayers for those injured in the terrorist attack today in London , \"","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"he administration said in a statement .","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"The president pledged to continue close collaboration with the United Kingdom","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"o stop attacks worldwide","depth":15},{"id":116,"text":"argeting innocent civilians","depth":15},{"id":117,"text":"nd to combat extremism . \"","depth":14},{"id":118,"text":"rump later said during a speech at Joint Base Andrews","depth":14},{"id":119,"text":"hat he expressed `` America ' s deepest sympathy as well as our absolute commitment","depth":16},{"id":120,"text":"o eradicating the terrorists from our planet ''","depth":16},{"id":121,"text":"o the British prime minister during the call .","depth":15},{"id":122,"text":"he president then vowed to eradicate `` radical Islamic terrorism . ''","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"he Islamic State claimed responsibility for the attacks just prior to Trump 's appearance .","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"rump also touted","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"hat the U.S. military 's capability could be `` both effective and overwhelming ''","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"n responding to the threat of terrorism and that of North Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"hich Thursday launched yet another ballistic missile over Japan ,","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"nflaming tensions in the region .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"rump and May also spoke of the recent North Korean nuclear test ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"ccording to a U.K. readout of the conversation ,","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"` agreeing","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"t was a reckless provocation","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"nd that China must now use all its leverage","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"o bring pressure to bear on the North Korean regime","depth":14},{"id":135,"text":"o ensure","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"hey change course","depth":16},{"id":137,"text":"nd end these illegal tests . \"","depth":16},{"id":138,"text":"arlier on Friday Trump had followed up his tweets on the London incident with one criticizing the administration of former President Barack Obama","depth":7},{"id":139,"text":"hile claiming success","depth":8},{"id":140,"text":"gainst fighting terrorists .","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"We have made more progress in the last nine months against ISIS","depth":9},{"id":142,"text":"han the Obama Administration has made in 8 years , \"","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"e said in the tweet .","depth":8},{"id":144,"text":"Must be proactive & nasty ! \"","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":289,"left":175,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":166,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":166,"left":160,"right":165,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":160,"left":151,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":0,"right":150,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":150,"left":1,"right":149,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":149,"left":147,"right":148,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":147,"left":2,"right":146,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":146,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":152,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":152,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":153,"right":11,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":153,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":157,"left":12,"right":156,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":156,"left":155,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nucl